Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:06.17,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Okizari ni shiteta futari deau made
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:10.48,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Nakushiteta nani ka
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:18.75,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Saigo no kakera wo torimodoshite
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:24.60,nhkop,Comment,0,0,0,,Aruki dasou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.94,0:01:39.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She appears to be an ordinary girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:44.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But in reality, she turns out to be a goddess
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.98,0:01:49.76,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Who has come to rescue the main\ncharacter from hikikomori.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:51.36,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:57.36,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:13.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:14.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\pos(80,226)\c&H000706&\3c&H101A18&\4a&HFF&\t(0,333,\c&H5C7381&\3c&HBDE5E1&)\t(6173,0,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&)}Gohan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:15.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:19.02,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You gotta respect those guys who make gal games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.02,0:02:22.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's amazing how they can come up with so\nmany different cute female characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.99,0:02:32.60,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm clueless when it comes to\nwhat girls are like in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:36.09,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So, when asked to make some characters,\NI naturally have my limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:41.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-san, I think you have misguided ideas\nat the fundamental level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.78,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you think the gal game users\nare looking for in the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:47.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,To escape reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.35,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,To escape reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:53.95,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna know why?\NBecause real life is filled with pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Girls who make fun of us men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.79,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Girls who look down on us men!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:02.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That fuckin' bitch who was cheating on me\nwith that convenience store manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.33,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That junior-college student\nwho toyed with my innocent youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Girls in real life are simply no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.94,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's precisely why it's essential\nthat girls in gal games
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:15.00,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,are made to suit our every whim and fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:20.11,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They fall in love with the main\ncharacter for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:23.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They approach the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.38,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They have no ulterior motives and never\nbetray the main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:34.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,We creators are obligated to create characters\nthat could not possibly exist in the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:38.73,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've got it, Yamazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:41.10,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I have a vision of the kind of\ncharacters I must create!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:44.00,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:48.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They fall in love with the main\ncharacter for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.91,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They approach the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.76,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H00181F&\4a&HFF&\3c&HBFF4FF&\fnSegoe Print\fs22\frz11.855\move(133,38,149,38,0,2848)}...no ulterior motives,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.76,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H00181F&\4a&HFF&\3c&HBFF4FF&\fnSegoe Print\fs22\frz11.855\move(174,100,190,100)}never betray the main character,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.76,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&H00181F&\4a&HFF&\3c&HBFF4FF&\fnSegoe Print\fs22\q2\frz11.855\move(194,172,210,172)}...characters that could not possibly exist in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.31,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They approach the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:54.01,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They have no ulterior motives and never\nbetray the main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:57.45,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Characters that could not possibly\nexist in the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.52,0:04:00.42,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This is exactly what I just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.96,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, popular characters in gal games\ntend to follow certain patterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, what are those patterns?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:12.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Pattern One!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.23,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.82,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:20.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,The fact that you've been good\nfriends since childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.34,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,helps develop a strong bond\nbetween the two of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:25.34,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You know we used to go see the\ncherry blossoms together a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Let your imagination do the work,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.74,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,and you can create heroines\nwho are perfect for you in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:37.41,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've always wanted things to be\nlike this with you, Tatchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:42.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Pattern Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:43.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She's a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.19,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:47.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Aren't maids kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.37,0:04:51.73,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Maids in the gal games are like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.44,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,A special aspect of the maids' occupation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.47,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,is that it entails a master-servant relationship\nbetween the main character and them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&}Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:04.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If there's anything you need, please\ndo not hesitate to ask, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,With that fantasy in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.58,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,you should be able to create ideal heroines\nwho are perfect for you in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:13.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.26,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, that's how it works, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.39,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Memo, memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:20.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And, Pattern Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.76,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:23.39,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:27.31,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I thought we were going to make a gal game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm talking about a humanoid robot like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:32.31,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She looks and functions just\nlike a real human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,However, she's a robot, so she\nwon't disobey humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.02,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.59,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I will execute your command.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.19,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,With that fantasy in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,you should be able to create ideal heroines\nwho are perfect for you in every way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:49.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I cannot be a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:52.76,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but I would like to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.44,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, that's how it works, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup, that's how it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.34,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Memo, memo...
