Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.38,0:06:13.72,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She approaches the main character innocently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:18.48,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I have come to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:23.22,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She has no ulterior motives and never\nbetrays the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:28.22,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, in fact it's perfect for my project\nif you're that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.09,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.81,0:06:44.44,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Ten more days till our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:57.36,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming up soon, Sato-kun.
