Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:14.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HEDECFC&\4a&HFF&\fnSegoe Script\b1\bord2\c&HA3A2E4&\q2\pos(187,232)}Do something instead of just sitting there and staring at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\3c&HEDECFC&\4a&HFF&\fnSegoe Script\b1\bord2\c&HA3A2E4&\pos(108,280)}Y-You can try to... k-kiss me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:19.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you just say something, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:23.48,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:27.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up? You're the one who said,\N"Let's play cards!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.53,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not talking about playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.53,0:07:35.13,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm talking about people beyond the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:37.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,or the atomic element that blocks light
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:41.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,or the fungus component contained in our food
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:43.47,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,or the viridian that has disappeared from the map...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:49.41,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That story again?! Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And most importantly, us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:58.52,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, you know something, Sato-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:04.79,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,There are conspiracies that we can\ndo nothing about in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:24.67,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If this was a game, I could do it\nas many times as I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.19,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:31.85,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But you tell me you haven't\ncome up with anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.55,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I gave you hints, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:38.20,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It should be easy if you just\nfollow those patterns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:39.33,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I know, but the thing is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.20,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have a beautiful childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:44.77,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's not like I can afford a maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.90,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Obviously, a robot is out of question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.51,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you still hung up on reality?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:52.71,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've already told you that you can't use girls from\nthe real world as references, haven't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:57.41,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But it'd still be easier for me to write the script\nif there were models and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.02,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Models?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:01.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,So you can write if there are models, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.65,0:09:04.26,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Y... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it! I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You can write if there are models, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.83,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I think I know where to go for that.\NLet's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:12.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm hikikomori, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:15.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been doing this for three years!\NI'm hard-core hikikomori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.27,0:09:18.80,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What makes you think that I'd go\noutside in broad daylight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:22.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But you went outside with no problem the other day!\NAnd you dragged me with you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't know what I was doing then!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:25.21,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be with you the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.61,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:31.52,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Then should I call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.58,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:37.66,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I've noticed that a lot of food's gone missing\nfrom my apartment lately.
