Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:43.39,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Including stuff like the instant ramen that I got from\nmy friend, stuff that's available only in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.66,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You know, that's an item hikikomori people would\nnever be able to get their hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:52.17,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Either you go with the police or go with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:53.84,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,One of the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:55.47,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Impossible... Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:59.74,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If you'd use some reason,\nall your impossibilities would go out the window!
