Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.58,0:11:43.08,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This is a sub-culture that Japan prides itself on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.38,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,They're called Maid Café's!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:47.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Maid Café?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.02,0:11:51.89,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It costs you a lot of money to\nhire a real maid at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:56.16,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless you're filthy rich, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:12:00.12,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But this place lets you enjoy being\na "master" at a reasonable price!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:05.16,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Maid Café's are a realization of the\ngal game players' dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.20,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:16.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Since we're already here, why don't we do some\nresearch on the market's trends and measures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.94,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
