Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:45.36,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel really lucky now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:47.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Get it the moment you see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.63,0:15:50.03,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That is the Golden Rule when you make\na pilgrimage to the Holy Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I see, the Golden Rule, huh?
