Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:04.14,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:06.51,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's a game character's '"fan disc."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It contains desktop accessories and mini-games.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:12.08,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Mini-games, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.14,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's hard to decide...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:19.86,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-san, remember the Golden Rule when you\nmake a pilgrimage to the Holy Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:21.46,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,"Get it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.59,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,"The moment you see it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.93,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I had no idea a world like this even existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.57,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Viva otaku culture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.57,0:16:32.00,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing can beat "moe"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:33.67,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Take a look at this figurine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:35.37,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.37,0:16:37.64,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's part of the DVD's special bonus, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.68,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Buying all five volumes together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.88,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive the rest of this month?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:43.51,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:46.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,For Pururin, I wouldn't mind dying from hunger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.02,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Look at you! You sure bought\na lot of stuff yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:52.75,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, Misao was calling me, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that everything you've ordered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.26,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Please enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.94,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's get to the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:13.01,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,"What would you need to make a gal game?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.38,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,To put it simply, it is "passion"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.75,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,No masterpiece is ever created without passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:18.62,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.89,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,However, things have gotten caught up in trends,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:24.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,and game content has become\noverly-uniform of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Honestly, I can't stand watching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:29.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You must absolutely respect the users' needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:32.16,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Doing what everybody else is doing\nwill never take you to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.03,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Therefore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.43,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,We must create something that\nappeals to the masses,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:39.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but at the same time something that would\ncompletely turn their world upside down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.74,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,In other words, we must continue to\nutilize the familiar patterns,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.94,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,but at the same time redefine them in a major way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.55,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:51.41,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Seeing you recognize that makes having\ntaken you to the Holy Land worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:55.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sato-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:18:01.05,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,The pilgrimage to the Holy Land has\nviolently energized my brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:05.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Something... Something new is\nabout to be born within me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.04,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.04,0:18:18.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I got an idea for the heroine of our game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:20.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:23.34,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend / classmate /\nnext door neighbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:26.95,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But the thing is, she's a robot, and\nnot only that, she's also a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.29,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:36.56,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:37.56,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.97,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's great! That's super moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I can feel my creative energy\nflowing through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.50,0:18:44.87,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna draw it up really quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.27,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, I wasn't done yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:50.78,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What's more, she was the main character's\ngirlfriend in his previous life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.98,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,That's excellent! It's super moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.28,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,On top of that, she's very sickly and the main\ncharacter is the only person she can rely on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This is incredible! It's so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Then she sacrifices herself in order\nto save him in a car accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.92,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,and suffered injuries that require a\nwhole year to fully recover from!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.92,0:19:04.05,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Excellent!
