Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:14.10,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,{\c&HFF6577&\4a&HFF&\bord2\fnSegoe Script\frx20\fry328\frz24.353\3c&HFFD1FF&\fscx191.25\fscy195\move(277,200,256,190,0,10344)}Millefeuille
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.49,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But the truth is that she's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.79,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's great!\NBut the truth is that she's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.82,0:19:09.33,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Not only that, she's an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:13.06,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,But her real identity turns out to be the\nreincarnation of a fox from space!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.66,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:25.78,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.15,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She's the heroine of our game!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:34.89,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,She's your childhood friend, a maid robot, sickly,\na ghost, an alien and an incarnation of a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:38.79,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, Sato-san, start writing the scenario\nusing this character!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.56,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.73,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I drew it just like you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.63,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,If you think about it from a normal standpoint,\nit's weird, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:52.50,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Dude, you're supposed to stop me\nand ask questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:56.00,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,We got kicked out of the café because you\nstarted going crazy all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.58,0:20:01.60,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn, I forgot something in the\nstore we were at earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.58,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:05.18,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Later...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.65,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.42,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:19.99,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,You wanna know how to get out of\nhikikomori, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:22.72,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tell you how once you sign the contract!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:30.70,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure you're okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:41.31,nhk,Comment,0,0,0,,Sato-kun?
